*"Shvataš* li da se osećaš srećno?" (Do you understand that you feel happy?)

*"Ne shvataš* li da je to problem?" (Don't you understand that this is a problem?)

*"Mislio sam da shvataš*." (I thought you understood.)

*"Da li shvataš* šta sam rekao?" (Do you understand what I said?)

*"On shvataš* da se mora razmisliti." (He understands that he has to think about it.)